---
title: "Phase B: Parallel Package Execution"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Coordinator
    participant A1 as Agent 1
    participant A2 as Agent 2

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over C,A2: wp-contracts runs first (no dependencies)
        A1->>C: get_work → wp-contracts
        A1->>C: acquire_lock(contract:openapi/v1.yaml)
        A1->>A1: Generate OpenAPI spec + types
        A1->>C: complete_work(result={openapi, types})
    end

    rect rgb(227, 242, 253)
        Note over C,A2: Backend + Frontend run in PARALLEL
        par
            A1->>C: get_work → wp-backend
            A1->>C: acquire_lock(src/api/*, db:schema:*)
            A1->>C: get_task(wp-contracts) → read result
            A1->>A1: Implement endpoints
            A1->>A1: Scope check + verify
            A1->>C: complete_work(backend result)
        and
            A2->>C: get_work → wp-frontend
            A2->>C: acquire_lock(src/ui/*)
            A2->>C: get_task(wp-contracts) → read result
            A2->>A2: Implement UI components
            A2->>A2: Scope check + verify
            A2->>C: complete_work(frontend result)
        end
    end

    Note over C,A2: Phase C: Merge worktrees → integration tests → merge queue
